Sentencas: Both Knudsen and bulk diffusion mechanisms are taken into account in the anode diffusivity measurement in solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs).
Titulo: An electrochemical device for the Knudsen and bulk diffusivity measurement in the anodes of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The correlation of anode parameters including pore size, porosity, tortuosity and thickness with the effective diffusivity is then explored analytically.
Titulo: An electrochemical device for the Knudsen and bulk diffusivity measurement in the anodes of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Through quantitative analysis, limiting current density and concentration polarization are investigated with various SOFC anode structures.
Titulo: An electrochemical device for the Knudsen and bulk diffusivity measurement in the anodes of solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Our work improves the understanding of the gas diffusion and electrochemical performances of SOFCs with various electrodes.
